<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="275" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1425,1702]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275">
<emphasis box="[199,291,1425,1450]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="275">Female.</emphasis>
Larger than males. Antenna of one measured specimen 
<quantity box="[946,1039,1425,1450]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.35" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" unit="cm" value="13.5">13.5 cm</quantity>
long. Tegmina small rounded and from each other separated lobes, reaching to abdominal tergite 
<number box="[878,895,1462,1486]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="2.0">2</number>
. Ovipositor stout at base, about half as long as body size, almost straight. Subgenital plate heart-shaped with circlic incision at posterior point.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1425,1702]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275">
<emphasis box="[199,368,1534,1557]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="275">Measurements,</emphasis>
male.— (mm) (N = 
<number box="[598,615,1534,1558]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="2.0">2</number>
). Body length: 
<number box="[787,860,1533,1558]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="26.5" valueMax="28.0" valueMin="25.0">25–28</number>
. Length of pronotum: 
<number box="[1110,1155,1533,1558]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="5.5" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="5.0">5–6</number>
. Length of visible part of elytra: 
<number box="[229,245,1569,1594]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="5.0">5</number>
. Length of hind femur: 
<number box="[512,586,1569,1594]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="29.0" valueMax="33.0" valueMin="25.0">25–33</number>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1425,1702]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275">
<emphasis box="[199,368,1606,1629]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="275">Measurements,</emphasis>
female.— (mm) (N = 
<number box="[622,638,1606,1630]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="3.0">3</number>
). Body length: 
<number box="[812,885,1606,1630]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="37.5" valueMax="42.0" valueMin="33.0">33–42</number>
. Length of pronotum: 
<number box="[1136,1153,1606,1629]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="7.0">7</number>
. Length of visible part of elytra: 
<number box="[229,274,1642,1666]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="3.5" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="3.0">3–4</number>
. Length of hind femur: 
<number box="[541,614,1641,1666]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="37.0" valueMax="39.0" valueMin="35.0">35–39</number>
. Ovipositor length: 
<number box="[836,910,1642,1666]" pageId="2" pageNumber="275" value="25.0" valueMax="28.0" valueMin="22.0">22–28</number>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
